<lyrics>[V1]
 1- sạjd ʿly̱ rkby qdạmk bạnzl
 wạ̉dy lk mkạnk
 ʿạbd bạtfrs fy jmạlk sạjd msẖtạq lltgẖyr
 ạlqrạr- sạjd dạ mkạn ạltgẖyyr lḥyạty wfḥṣ
 ạlḍmyr
